simply go to UICcareers.com , go to “Employer” to register your organization. Once in the system, managed by Symplicity.com, you may request your preferred date(s) and the number of rooms you may need for a particular day. Once approved, and the information is posted, you may pre-select candidates for your schedule(s).  Interviews take place at our UIC Career Services offices with private interview rooms, convenient parking (we will validate your parking upon request), as well as complimentary coffee or tea.  You may also request this service by contacting Cindy Graham, Assistant Director for Employer Relations, at cgraham1@uic.edu or (312) 355-4047.       on campus        UIC Careers Website          Employers    Back to main content           Post A Position    UICcareers    Career Fair Information for Employers    On-Campus Interviews    Information Tables & Sessions    Employer Partner Program    Additional Outreach & Student Engagement Opportunities    Directions / Hotels                  UIC Logo        Career Services         Students    Career Planning Guide    Make an Appointment    FAQs      Employers    Post a Position    UICcareers.com      Campus Partners    Campus Partners    Program/Workshop Request Forms        Footer Menu    Career Programs and Events    UICcareers    UIC Student Employment Office         Contact   Suite 3050 1200 West Harrison Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996-2300  Fax: (312) 413-0383  careerservices@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 